<article class="prose">
  <h1>Privacy</h1>
  <p>
    CoCitizen does not collect personal data and does not use third-party analytics or
    tracking scripts.
  </p>
  <p>
    This site is hosted on
    <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Pages</a>.
    Cloudflare collects aggregate, anonymized visitor statistics — page views and general
    traffic patterns. No personal information, browsing history, or identifying data is
    collected or retained. We don't care and are too lazy to look anyway. 
  </p>
  <p>
    Contact is by email only. We don't operate web forms and don't store submissions.
  </p>
  <p>
    Links to GitHub point to GitHub.com. Their
    <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener">privacy policy</a>
    applies to those pages.
  </p>
</article>
